      <p>"Here, Sirko, eat your fill! This is to thank you for saving our baby."
  
      <p>Evening came, the master and mistress went home, and they took Sirko
      with them. They went in to the house, and the master said:
  
      <p>" Make us an extra dish of dumplings, wife, and don't spare the fat!"
      
      <p>The dumplings were soon ready, and the master seated Sirko at the
